37 Paramount Drive, Wangara is fully leased to a multi-national tenant until 4th June 2021, representing a unique investment opportunity that will not last. Located within the established industrial precinct of Wangara this well-presented facility features functional office space, clean and well maintained workshop and dual crossovers.

KEY FEATURES:
• Office: 396sqm*
• Workshop: 1,336sqm*
• Hardstand: 500sqm*
• 7.3% annual return
• Proximity to Hartman Drive and Ocean Reef Road
• Functional office/workshop improvements
• Hardstand laydown

LEASE SUMMARY
• Lessee: Pentair Flow Control Pacific (Int company)
• Lease Term: Expires 4th June 2021 + 5-year option
• Annual Rent: $207,344.07pa + outgoings and GST
• Reviews: CPI from 2018-2020 - Market in 2021

To make the most of this rare investment opportunity, please contact one of the exclusive selling agents.

*approx

58 Prosperity Avenue features a modern office/workshop facility plus fully secured hardstand.  This unique hardstand component, fully enclosed with high bay concrete elevations and partly covered by an overhead canopy makes it the perfect low cost dispatch warehouse to accompany the main workshop.
 

KEY FEATURES:
• Ground Floor Office: 103sqm*
• First Floor Office: 140sqm*
• Mezzanine Storage: 54sqm*
• Workshop: 868sqm*
• Covered/Secured Hardstand: 600sqm*
• 4 x Roller Doors
• Proximity to Ocean Reef Road and Hartman Drive
• Dual street access
• Three Kitchenettes
• 3 Phase Power
• Compressed Air
• CCTV Security Cameras
• 27 Car bays
• Outgoings $30,000 per annum*

This property is located within the established industrial precinct of Wangara within close proximity to Ocean Reef Road, benefiting from multiple roller door access and dual crossovers to Prosperity Avenue. 

For further information or to arrange a viewing, please contact the exclusive leasing agents.
